msgctxt "sn22.81:8.1"
msgid "Na heva kho rūpaṃ attato samanupassati, na rūpavantaṃ attānaṃ samanupassati, na attani rūpaṃ samanupassati; "
msgstr "Perhaps they don’t regard form as self, or self as possessing form, or form in self, "

